---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Accessibility Statement">
    <main class="legal-page">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Accessibility Statement</h1>
            <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: February 2026</p>

            <div class="legal-content">
                <section>
                    <h2>1. Our Commitment</h2>
                    <p>
                        The Salon is committed to ensuring digital accessibility
                        for people with disabilities. We are continually
                        improving the user experience for everyone and applying
                        the relevant accessibility standards.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2>2. Measures to Support Accessibility</h2>
                    <p>
                        The Salon takes the following measures to ensure
                        accessibility of our website:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Include accessibility as part of our mission
                            statement.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Integrate accessibility into our procurement
                            practices.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Appoint an accessibility officer and/or ombudsperson
                            to answer questions about access concerns.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Provide continual accessibility training for our
                            staff.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2>3. Conformance Status</h2>
                    <p>
                        The Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) defines
                        requirements for designers and developers to improve
                        accessibility for people with disabilities. It defines
                        three levels of conformance: Level A, Level AA, and
                        Level AAA. The Salon website is partially conformant
                        with WCAG 2.1 Level AA. Partially conformant means that
                        some parts of the content do not fully conform to the
                        accessibility standard.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2>4. Feedback</h2>
                    <p>
                        We welcome your feedback on the accessibility of The
                        Salon's website. Please let us know if you encounter
                        accessibility barriers on our site:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            E-mail: <a
                                href="mailto:accessibility@thesalon.london"
                                >accessibility@thesalon.london</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>Phone: +44 20 7123 4567</li>
                        <li>
                            Visitor address: 123 Oxford Street, London, W1D 1LP
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>We try to respond to feedback within 2 business days.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .legal-page {
        padding-top: 140px;
        padding-bottom: 4rem;
        min-height: 80vh;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .last-updated {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .legal-content {
        background: var(--color-surface);
        padding: 3rem;
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        max-width: 900px;
    }

    section {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
        color: var(--color-accent);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    ul {
        list-style: disc;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    }

    li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .legal-content {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
